OUTLIER CHARACTERIZATION
------------------------------------------------------------

🔴 PHYSICAL JUSTIFICATION:
   • 23 structures with POSITIVE energies removed
     Range: [20.25, 816.51]
     → Positive energies are unphysical for stable proteins
   • 43 structures with extreme high energies (>5σ from clean data mean)
     Clean data mean: -322.13 ± 14.46
   • 79 structures with RMSD > 10Å
     Max RMSD: 16.59Å
     → These represent completely misfolded decoys

📊 STATISTICAL JUSTIFICATION:
   • Removal percentage: 3.8%
     → Well within acceptable limits (<5-10%)
   • Multi-method consensus: 6 independent methods
   • Consensus threshold: flagged by ≥2 methods
   • This ensures robust, non-arbitrary removal

📈 IMPACT ON CORRELATION:
   Before removal: r = 0.4344 (p = 1.3440e-115)
   After removal:  r = 0.6990 (p = 0.0000e+00)
   Improvement:    ++0.2646 (60.9%)
   → Removal reveals true funnel relationship obscured by artifacts

